openmediavault (0.4.7-2) precise; urgency=low

  * Added following dependencies:
    - php-json-schema
    - php5-auth-pam
    - ethtool
  * Added 'make-ssl-cert generate-default-snakeoil --force-overwrite' if
    neither the self-signed certification or key exists on the system already
  * Added ubuntu_02_apache_extjs_location.patch to look for extjs directory
    instead of extjs3. This will need to be changed in the future if OMV
    decides to switch to extjs4

 -- Richard A. Johnson <nixternal@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Jan 2013 12:12:23 -0600

openmediavault (0.4.7-1) precise; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * Patches:
    - ubuntu_01_samba_to_smbd.diff - change init.d/samba references to
    init.d/smbd. Fixes the 'invoke-rc.d: unknown initscript' install issue

 -- Richard A. Johnson <nixternal@gmail.com>  Thu, 13 Dec 2012 13:47:56 -0600
